textBody:
The Power of Love or Power of Love may refer to:

Film and television

*The Power of Love (film), an early 3D film demonstrated in 1922
*"The Power of Love", an episode of The O.C. (season 2) (2005)
*"The Power of Love", an episode of Degrassi: The Next Generation (2004)

Music

Albums

*The Power of Love (Fish Leong album), 2003
*The Power of Love (Sam Bailey album), 2014
*Power of Love (Hour Glass album), 1967
*Power of Love (Luther Vandross album), 1991
*Harry and the Potters and the Power of Love, 2006
*Power of Love, by Arlo Guthrie, 1981
*The Power of Love, by Captain Sensible, 1984

Songs

*"The Power of Love", a composition by Percy Grainger
*"The Power of Love" (Charley Pride song)
*"The Power of Love" (Frankie Goes to Hollywood song) (1984), also covered by Gabrielle Aplin, 2012
*"The Power of Love" (Huey Lewis and the News song)
*"The Power of Love" (Jennifer Rush song) (1985), also covered by Laura Branigan and Céline Dion
*"(You Got) The Power of Love", by The Everly Brothers, also covered by Nancy Wilson
*"Power of Love/Love Power", by Luther Vandross
*"The Power of Love", by 10cc from Ten Out of 10
*"The Power of Love", by After the Anthems
*"The Power of Love", by Corona
*"The Power of Love", by Ray Conniff
*"Power of Love" (Joe Simon song), also covered by Martha Reeves
*"Power of Love", by Mahavishnu Orchestra, the opening track from their album Apocalypse
*"Power of Love" (Deee-Lite song)
*"Power of Love", by Gary Wright from The Dream Weaver
*"Power of Love", a song by Judy and Mary
*"The Power of Love", a song by Michael Benghiat, John Miyagi Author, and Evan Roberts; sung by Jennifer Cihi

Similar titles

*"Faith (In the Power of Love)", song by Rozalla
*Heaven, Heartache, and the Power of Love, album by Trisha Yearwood
**"Heaven, Heartache, and the Power of Love" (song), its titular song
*"I Have Learned to Respect the Power of Love", 1985 song by Stephanie Mills
*The Power of Your Love, album by Hillsong Church
*Pyar Kare Dis: Feel the Power of Love, 2007 Sindhi film
*"Respect the Power of Love", song by Namie Amuro
*"Two to the Power of Love", song by Janet Jackson and Cliff Richard
